Missing features (broken at runtime):
- useManualVoiceInput called /api/sessions/{id}/transcribe which did NOT exist in
  any backend route — added app/api/transcribe.py REST endpoint that accepts audio
  file uploads, attempts pydub/PyAV decoding, and falls back to raw bytes passthrough
- useManualTTS called /api/tts/speak which also did NOT exist — added POST /tts/speak
  endpoint in tts_metrics.py; collects PCM from tts_service.stream_synthesize, wraps
  in WAV container, returns as audio/wav for browser <audio> playback
- stt_ws.py and tts_ws.py routers were never registered in main.py — now registered
  as /ws/stt/{session_id} and /ws/tts/{session_id}

WebSocket accept order:
- stt_ws.py had same send_json-before-accept bug as interview_ws.py — fixed

audioop deprecation (Python 3.13 removal):
- stt_service.py also imported audioop for PCM resampling
- Extracted shared _resample_pcm_s16le into new app/services/audio_utils.py
- Both stt_service.py and sensevoice_stt_service.py now import from audio_utils
- Eliminates code duplication, makes the resampler unit-testable in isolation

Tests:
- Added 8 new tests in test_new_fixes.py (21 total, all passing):
  TestAssertSessionOwner: 404/403/ownership pass
  TestResamplePcm: identity, downsample, upsample, empty, s16le validity
