Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fixes:
- useWebSocket.ts: replace btoa(String.fromCharCode(...new Uint8Array(chunk)))
  with 8192-byte chunked loop — spread on large TypedArrays throws
  'Maximum call stack size exceeded' for audio buffers > ~256 KB
- backend/.env.example: sync TTS_FIRST_CHUNK_TIMEOUT_SECONDS (6.5→5.0) and
  TTS_HEDGE_DELAY_SECONDS (0.85→0.55) to match README performance recommendations
- backend/.env.example: change DATABASE_URL default to SQLite so new contributors
  can run the project immediately without provisioning PostgreSQL

Docs:
- README.md: comprehensive rewrite covering all 15 bug fixes, new API endpoints
  (/api/sessions/{id}/transcribe, /api/tts/speak, WebSocket routes), updated
  system architecture diagram, complete API reference table, and change log
